Package runner

Class AlgorithmBenchmarker

  • java.lang.Object
    • runner.AlgorithmBenchmarker
  • public class AlgorithmBenchmarker
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which stores the result of benchmarking algorithms. Can store the results of more than one benchmark run and calculate various statistics (mean, sigma) for reporting and analysis
    Author:
    ksomers
